media:group.media:title: Rune Factory 5 :: Unboxing & Discussion
media:group.media:description:
Please join me in my ramblings about the joys of Rune Factory and the new game RF5.

Time Stamps:
00:00 Intro
03:00 Topic no. 1 and no. 2
07:30 comparison of RF5 and RF4 boxes
08:55 NZ age rating "M"
11:00 Box open!
13:30 The Rune Factory formula
16:10 Topic no. 2
20:25 The background story to RF5
21:30 The art book
23:10 Issues around environment design
25:45 Rune Factory continues!
26:10 Wrap up

Music: from the Rune Factory 5 OST

Rune Factory 5 is rated PEGI 12 for Europe, T (for Teen) for North America, and M (Mature 17+) for New Zealand. 
My video is therefore NOT suitable for children as per the COPPA legislation.
